hkgmoji\" /><br />\n必在 11月 24日 7:30am 前，在facebook發表，證明已為<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">7－11pm</span></strong>活動申請不反通知書，先發表就出線有票，遲發表要退選。</span><br />\n撞區表 <a href=\"https://hkfactcheck.io/crashes/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkfactcheck.io%2Fcrashes%2F1&d=SNVPshlwtiHAgFu1pF0TpOQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=175187b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkfactcheck.io/crashes/1</a><br />\n<br />\n誠邀：曾出席『<span style=\"color: red;\">民主歌聲獻中華</span>』演藝人、所有民主派議員、及候選人。〔民主派即是所有推動民主，包括本土及泛民〕<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span><br />\n<br />\n11.24 民主歌聲獻香港 圍繞理大走一圈 【和理非行動post】<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1747254\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1747254</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">幫幫手推一推行動post拉！連登重有邊個唔去投票！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n下期預告：12.1 民主歌聲撐林夕 圍繞理大走一圈 【行動post】"},{"pid":"77091072840b8f30fc0d42e583cf17aa93c8668c","tid":1747963,"uid":241093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T14:30:42.000Z","msg":"1124記得投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8127c74b4a009ab6b3cadb642319c717902b2718","tid":1747963,"uid":241093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T14:36:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/SPHwTN0ydIY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FSPHwTN0ydIY&d=SNVPshlwtiHAgFu1pF0TpOQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=2d318917\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/SPHwTN0ydIY</a>"},{"pid":"13c5fe115d20ddf9e0fd2535bd4da6dfd0d